2026-05-12T22:34:10.0920972Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-12T22:34:10.0922107Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-12T22:34:10.0922841Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-05-12T22:34:10.0923426Z 19        we only request it when the toggle is on.
2026-05-12T22:34:10.0923853Z 20    -->
2026-05-12T22:34:10.0924654Z 21    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_FULL_SCREEN_INTENT" />
