2026-05-12T22:34:10.0926433Z 21-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:16:22-78
2026-05-12T22:34:10.0927021Z 22    <!--
2026-05-12T22:34:10.0927454Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-12T22:34:10.0927997Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-12T22:34:10.0928499Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-12T22:34:10.0929119Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-12T22:34:10.0929730Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-12T22:34:10.0931280Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-12T22:34:10.0932037Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-12T22:34:10.0932791Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-12T22:34:10.0933466Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-12T22:34:10.0934083Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-12T22:34:10.0934584Z 33    -->
2026-05-12T22:34:10.0935147Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
